&lt;h2 id="how-can-we-remove-aminopyralid-weedkiller-from-the-soil">How can we remove aminopyralid weedkiller from the soil&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>In a wet ground, it will break down into harmless compound.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It will take some time, though, dependent on the moisture in the soil and the temperature.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>See &lt;a href="#how-to-heal-the-contaminated-soil">below for more details&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>
